44:09.160 --> 44:12.360
Oh, is that what you think I am?
A Neanderthal surfer?

44:12.360 --> 44:16.080
Oh, no! Of course not.

44:29.600 --> 44:33.960
Do you know what I mean?
We've gotta fight the fight, Tracy.

44:33.960 --> 44:35.840
Gotta fight it.

44:39.400 --> 44:40.680
Hey.

44:40.680 --> 44:42.800
Look, I don't know what you think
you saw, but Tash is just...

44:42.800 --> 44:44.280
