that's not about me?

45:00.000 --> 45:02.480
No, I... Yes, I...

45:02.480 --> 45:04.680
Look, this is really confusing
for me.

45:04.680 --> 45:06.080
For YOU?

45:06.080 --> 45:07.760
I just...I wish that hadn't happened,
